{"tid":1677992,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"馬嶽稱不再為應徵警隊學生寫推薦信","createTime":"2019-10-27T12:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T14:31:05.000Z","uid":155883,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc02c831d162521f8226f5aa1814c0fcf13c11b","tid":1677992,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10152825393042448/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.170516952447%2F10152825393042448%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=0afcab04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10152825393042448/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n昨日傍晚至今，警方在多處地方施放催淚彈對付示威者，示威者仍於金鐘、旺角及銅鑼灣多處聚集。中大政治與行政學系副教授馬嶽昨晚於社交網站發表聲明，表示從今以後不會再替同學寫應徵警隊的推薦信。"},{"pid":"518224de90f0151d60376ea1e163d7ed69c1ecd7","tid":1677992,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:01:21.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03807608f1eced385c499fefba44e27cb38875b8","tid":1677992,"uid":332229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdc02c831d162521f8226f5aa1814c0fcf13c11b","tid":1677992,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10152825393042448/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.170516952447%2F10152825393042448%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=0afcab04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10